name: Yotsuyu (Final fantasy XIV) - LoRA - Realistic
description:
Yotsuyu goe Brutus is a character in Final Fantasy XIV: Stormblood, and serves as its tertiary antagonist. She is the main antagonist of post-Stormblood patches. She is the acting imperial viceroy of Doma.

I trained this Lora model using dozens of in-game screenshots by NED.

You can use this Lora on different models to get some Realistic/2.5D images.

Checkpoint recommendation

2.5D model: NeverEndDream

Realistic suggest: majicMIX realistic v4/v5

weight 0.6~0.8

You can tag striped, kimono, jewelry, neckwear to get her in-game costume.

TAG long_hair, bangs, black_hair, mole under mouth, head flower,

More pic in my twi: Change@LianReen
